---
import TellLayout from '../layouts/TellLayout.astro';
---

<TellLayout title="TIAM CLINIC 福利厚生 | 採用力と社員満足度を最大化">
  <section class="hero-bg pt-32 pb-20 md:pt-48 md:pb-32 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-20 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-pink-100 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-70 animate-pulse"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-40 left-0 w-72 h-72 bg-yellow-100 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-70 animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 1s;"></div>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="text-left fade-in-up is-visible">
          <span class="inline-block py-1 px-4 rounded-full bg-black text-white text-xs font-bold tracking-wider mb-6">美容医療サブスクリプションのご提案</span>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 mb-6 leading-[1.2]">
            社員の<span class="text-pink-500">採用力</span>と<br /><span class="text-pink-500">満足度</span>を高める<br /><span class="text-[#d4a373]">美容福利厚生</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            給与アップよりもコスト効率が高く、即戦力人材に響く。<br /><strong>月額16,500円</strong>の定額導入で、<br />社員全員が美容医療を<strong>40%OFF</strong>で受けられる新しい仕組み。
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <a href="https://page.line.me/718awdjv" target="_blank" class="bg-[#06c755] hover:bg-[#05b34c] text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-lg font-bold shadow-lg text-center transition transform hover:-translate-y-1 flex items-center justify-center">
              <i data-lucide="message-circle" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 fill-current"></i> LINEで導入相談
            </a>
            <a href="#plan" class="bg-white text-gray-800 border border-gray-200 px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-lg font-bold shadow-sm text-center hover:bg-gray-50 transition">プラン詳細を見る</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative fade-in-up is-visible" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
          <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border-8 border-white transform rotate-2 hover:rotate-0 transition duration-500">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1629909613654-28e377c37b09?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2068&q=80" alt="クリニックのイメージ" class="w-full h-auto object-cover" />
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow-xl flex items-center gap-3 animate-bounce">
            <div class="bg-pink-100 p-2 rounded-full"><i data-lucide="gem" class="h-6 w-6 text-pink-500"></i></div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-bold">従業員満足度</p>
              <p class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">向上・定着率UP</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-stone-50 py-12 border-b border-gray-200">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-500 mb-6 tracking-wider">OFFICIAL SNS ACCOUNT</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6">
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/tiam_ginza" target="_blank" class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition hover:scale-105 group">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-tr from-yellow-400 via-pink-500 to-purple-600 text-white p-1.5 rounded-full"><i data-lucide="instagram" class="w-5 h-5"></i></div>
          <div class="text-left"><span class="block text-xs text-gray-400 font-bold">Instagram</span><span class="font-bold text-gray-800 group-hover:text-pink-600 transition">Follower 2.6万+</span></div>
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@tiamclinicginza/videos" target="_blank" class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition hover:scale-105 group">
          <div class="bg-red-600 text-white p-1.5 rounded-full"><i data-lucide="youtube" class="w-5 h-5"></i></div>
          <div class="text-left"><span class="block text-xs text-gray-400 font-bold">YouTube</span><span class="font-bold text-gray-800 group-hover:text-red-600 transition">Official Channel</span></div>
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@tiam_clinic" target="_blank" class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition hover:scale-105 group">
          <div class="bg-black text-white p-1.5 rounded-full"><svg class="w-5 h-5 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12.525.02c1.31-.02 2.61-.01 3.91-.02.08 1.53.63 3.09 1.75 4.17 1.12 1.11 2.7 1.62 4.24 1.79v4.03c-1.44-.05-2.89-.35-4.2-.97-.57-.26-1.1-.65-1.62-1.12-1.41-1.29-2.3-3.08-2.68-4.96h-3.62c-.06 6.55-.02 13.11.02 19.67.04 1.52-.36 3.09-1.22 4.37-1.42 2.05-4.07 3.29-6.52 2.87-2.62-.43-4.75-2.52-5.17-5.16-.4-2.43.83-5.06 2.87-6.49 1.28-.9 2.87-1.31 4.43-1.14v4.13c-.9-.12-1.84.14-2.55.76-.71.63-1.07 1.57-1.01 2.51.09 1.35 1.34 2.47 2.68 2.39 1.29-.08 2.42-1.09 2.52-2.38.16-2.12.06-4.25.07-6.38.01-6.07 0-12.14-.02-18.21z"/></svg></div>
          <div class="text-left"><span class="block text-xs text-gray-400 font-bold">TikTok</span><span class="font-bold text-gray-800 group-hover:text-black transition">Official Account</span></div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="about" class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center fade-in-up">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">こんな<span class="text-pink-500">お悩み</span>はありませんか？</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 mb-12">人材確保の難易度が上がる中、従来の対策では限界がきています。</p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-2xl hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300">
          <div class="bg-white w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 shadow-sm"><i data-lucide="users" class="h-8 w-8 text-gray-400"></i></div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">採用競争の激化</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">求人募集を出しても同業他社との差別化が難しく、優秀な人材が集まらない。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-2xl hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300">
          <div class="bg-white w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 shadow-sm"><i data-lucide="trending-up" class="h-8 w-8 text-gray-400"></i></div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">給与アップの限界</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">給与を上げても社会保険や税金の負担が重く、社員の手取りは思ったほど増えない。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-2xl hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300">
          <div class="bg-white w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 shadow-sm"><i data-lucide="bar-chart-3" class="h-8 w-8 text-gray-400"></i></div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">福利厚生費の増大</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">一般的な福利厚生は「人数 × コスト」。社員が増えるほど負担が青天井に。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="comparison" class="py-24 bg-stone-100 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 fade-in-up">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">なぜ、この福利厚生が選ばれるのか？</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">視覚的にわかる「圧倒的なコストパフォーマンス」</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="fade-in-up" id="graph-trigger">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6 border-l-4 border-[#d4a373] pl-4">コストは一定、満足度は上昇</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 text-sm">一般的な福利厚生は社員数に比例してコストが増大します。<br />対して、TIAM CLINICは<strong>人数無制限で定額</strong>。社員が増えるほどお得になります。</p>
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <div>
              <div class="flex justify-between text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 mb-2"><span>一般的な福利厚生 (人数比例)</span><span>コスト増大</span></div>
              <div class="bar-container"><div class="bar-fill bg-gray-400" data-width="95%"><span class="text-white text-xs font-bold px-2">High Cost</span></div></div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="flex justify-between text-xs font-bold text-[#d4a373] mb-2"><span>TIAM CLINIC (定額制)</span><span>コスト一定</span></div>
              <div class="bar-container"><div class="bar-fill bg-[#d4a373] relative shadow-lg" data-width="30%"><div class="absolute -right-2 -top-10 bg-[#d4a373] text-white text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded animate-bounce">圧倒的低コスト<div class="absolute top-full left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 border-4 border-transparent border-t-[#d4a373]"></div></div><span class="text-white text-xs font-bold px-2">Fixed Cost</span></div></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="fade-in-up" id="balance-trigger">
          <div class="text-center mb-4"><span class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-500 bg-white/80 inline-block px-4 py-1 rounded-full backdrop-blur-sm shadow-sm">同じコストをかけるなら…？</span></div>
          <div class="balance-container">
            <div class="balance-pole"></div>
            <div class="balance-base"></div>
            <div class="balance-arm" id="balance-arm">
              <div class="plate-left-group">
                <div class="plate-string"></div>
                <div class="plate bg-gray-200 border-2 border-gray-300" id="plate-left"><span class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-500">給与UP</span><span class="text-[10px] text-gray-400 mt-1">税負担大</span></div>
              </div>
              <div class="plate-right-group">
                <div class="plate-string"></div>
                <div class="plate bg-[#d4a373] border-4 border-white z-20" id="plate-right"><i data-lucide="sparkles" class="text-white w-6 h-6 mb-1"></i><span class="text-xs font-bold text-white">福利厚生</span><span class="text-[9px] text-white/90 mt-0.5">満足度大</span></div>
                <div class="absolute -top-10 -right-10 text-2xl animate-pulse">✨</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="new-value" class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-stone-50 to-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 fade-in-up">
        <span class="text-[#d4a373] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm">Beyond Benefits</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-2">福利厚生は「守り」から<br /><span class="text-[#d4a373]">「攻め」</span>の投資へ</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">人手不足対策だけではありません。<br />美容医療への投資は、社員の自信を引き出し、ビジネスの現場で「価値ある」人材を育成します。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="fade-in-up">
          <div class="mb-10">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center"><span class="bg-[#d4a373] text-white w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 text-sm font-bold">01</span>ハロー効果で印象アップ</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4"><strong>「ハロー効果」</strong>とは、外見などの目立ちやすい特徴が、その人の全体評価に影響を与える心理現象です。清潔感のある外見は、ビジネスにおける信頼感の向上につながると言われています。</p>
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
              <ul class="space-y-3">
                <li class="flex items-start"><i data-lucide="check-circle-2" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#d4a373] mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0"></i><span class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-800">清潔感のある外見 <span class="text-gray-400 mx-1">→</span> 「信頼できる」という印象へ</span></li>
                <li class="flex items-start"><i data-lucide="check-circle-2" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#d4a373] mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0"></i><span class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-800">肌の調子が良い <span class="text-gray-400 mx-1">→</span> 「自己管理ができている」印象へ</span></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center"><span class="bg-[#d4a373] text-white w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 text-sm font-bold">02</span>自信が行動を変える</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">コンプレックスが解消されると、人は自然と積極的になります。内面から湧き出る自信は、仕事へのモチベーション向上やパフォーマンスアップに繋がります。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative fade-in-up" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-full p-8 shadow-2xl aspect-square flex items-center justify-center relative max-w-md mx-auto">
            <div class="text-center z-10"><p class="text-sm text-gray-400 font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-1">POSITIVE CYCLE</p><p class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">好循環の<br />創出</p></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full animate-[spin_20s_linear_infinite]">
              <div class="absolute top-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-24 h-24 bg-pink-50 rounded-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center shadow-md animate-[spin_20s_linear_infinite_reverse]"><i data-lucide="sparkles" class="w-6 h-6 text-pink-500 mb-1"></i><span class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-700 text-center">外見への<br />自信</span></div>
              <div class="absolute top-1/2 right-4 translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-24 h-24 bg-blue-50 rounded-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center shadow-md animate-[spin_20s_linear_infinite_reverse]"><i data-lucide="zap" class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-500 mb-1"></i><span class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-700 text-center">積極的な<br />行動</span></div>
              <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 translate-y-1/2 w-24 h-24 bg-green-50 rounded-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center shadow-md animate-[spin_20s_linear_infinite_reverse]"><i data-lucide="trophy" class="w-6 h-6 text-green-500 mb-1"></i><span class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-700 text-center">意欲・<br />評価UP</span></div>
              <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-4 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-24 h-24 bg-yellow-50 rounded-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center shadow-md animate-[spin_20s_linear_infinite_reverse]"><i data-lucide="smile" class="w-6 h-6 text-yellow-500 mb-1"></i><span class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-700 text-center">自己肯定感<br />向上</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur px-6 py-2 rounded-full shadow-lg border border-gray-100 whitespace-nowrap"><i data-lucide="trending-up" class="inline w-4 h-4 text-[#d4a373] mr-2"></i><span class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-700">美容は「価値ある自己投資」です</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="director" class="py-24 bg-white relative">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 fade-in-up">
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#d4a373] transform translate-x-4 translate-y-4 rounded-xl"></div>
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1612349317150-e413f6a5b16d?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1470&q=80" alt="院長イメージ" class="relative rounded-xl shadow-lg w-full object-cover h-[400px] bg-gray-200" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full md:w-2/3 fade-in-up" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
          <span class="text-[#d4a373] font-bold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-2 block">Director Message</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 font-serif">10年後も通ってよかったと言っていただける<br />「美容の町医者」を目指して</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">クリニック名のTIAM（ティアム）はペルシア語で「初めて出会った時の、目の輝き」という意味を持ちます。<br />新たな自分に出会い目を輝かせる一瞬、そしてその輝きが自信となり、人生をより豊かにしていく。<br />そんなお手伝いがしたいという想いで、このクリニックを開院しました。</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">私は元々麻酔科医としてキャリアをスタートさせました。「痛みが怖い」という患者様の不安を誰よりも理解しています。<br />だからこそ、脂肪吸引や糸リフトといった施術においても、麻酔科医としての知識を活かし、痛みに最大限配慮した安全な医療を提供することをお約束します。<br />福利厚生を通じて、働く皆様の「自信」と「笑顔」を引き出すことができれば幸いです。</p>
          <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-6">
            <p class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">TIAM CLINIC GINZA 理事長</p>
            <p class="text-2xl font-serif text-[#d4a373] mt-1">谷口 弘樹 <span class="text-base text-gray-500 font-sans ml-2">Hiroki Taniguchi</span></p>
            <div class="mt-4 text-xs text-gray-500 space-y-1"><p>・福井大学医学部 卒業</p><p>・麻酔科標榜医 取得</p><p>・大手美容外科、大学病院整形外科を経て現職</p></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="quality" class="py-24 bg-stone-900 text-white relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full overflow-hidden z-0 opacity-20">
      <div class="absolute -top-20 -left-20 w-96 h-96 bg-[#d4a373] rounded-full blur-[100px]"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-80 h-80 bg-pink-600 rounded-full blur-[100px]"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 fade-in-up">
        <span class="text-[#d4a373] font-serif italic text-2xl">Our Quality</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mt-2">福利厚生だからこそ、<br class="md:hidden" />「本物」を提供したい</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">安かろう悪かろうではありません。<br />大切な社員様をお預かりする責任を持って、質の高いサービスを提供します。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 p-8 rounded-2xl hover:bg-white/20 transition duration-300 fade-in-up">
          <div class="mb-6"><span class="bg-[#d4a373] text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">DOCTOR</span><h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-3">痛みへの配慮と<br />確かな美的センス</h3></div>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">麻酔科医出身の院長監修のもと、痛みに最大限配慮した施術を追求。小顔形成や美肌治療において、結果にこだわる治療を提供します。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 p-8 rounded-2xl hover:bg-white/20 transition duration-300 fade-in-up" style="transition-delay: 0.1s;">
          <div class="mb-6"><span class="bg-pink-500 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">NURSE</span><h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-3">厳しい試験を突破した<br />技術力</h3></div>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">独自の厳しい合格基準を満たすまで、患者様を担当することはありません。最新機器の照射技術や安全管理を徹底的に習得したプロフェッショナルが担当します。</p>
